A company plans to set up a bucket ACL in Amazon S3 to allow users to list all the objects in the tutorialsdojo bucket and retrieve them. The CloudOps Engineer prepared the below policy using the AWS Policy Generator. What will happen if the Administrator applies this bucket policy in S3?

{
"Id": "TutorialsDojo.com S3 Policy",
"Version": "2012-10-17",
"Statement": [
{
"Sid": "TutsDojo_S3_GetObject_and_ListBucket_Policy",
"Action": [
"s3:GetObject",
"s3:ListBucket"
],
"Effect": "Allow",
"Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::tutorialsdojo",
"Principal": "*"
}
]
}
